data.description: Lot Value Only. Build your perfect getaway that's still close to everything. Hidden gem...lot is almost an acre located along White Oak Bayou. The neighborhood is small and quiet with little to no traffic. Just minutes away from the park, shopping, dining, biking and walking trails, dog park, and so much more. Call to make an appointment today. Do not disturb tenants. Dogs are on property.
